@NODE Introduction
@TITLE Introduction

   Well, I'm writing this guide due to some inspiration from a good friend
of mine, John Forrest.  He is the SYSOP of @{"BrainScan BBS" link BBS}.
Because I am connected to the Internet, and I use BBS's ( I'm CO-SYSOP of
BrainScan BBS ) I kept using abreviations, which IRC people would recognise
from me, but BBS people wouldn't, so, the primary reason for this guide is
to tell people what abreviations I use stand for.  But, seeing as I'm
actually doing this at the same time as editing my @{"Web pages" link
Contact}
I 'spose I'll put some effort into it.  Well, take a look around.  You may
be surprised!

Click on @{"Contents" link main} and go back then ;)




