@NODE AboutMe
@TITLE "About Bradley Smith"


Well, My name is Bradley David Smith.  I'm 15 years old, and my Birthday is
on the 21st June.  I live in Welwyn Garden City, Hertfordshire, England.
I'm an outgoing, friendly person, and I enjoy social activities - yes, in
other words, going out with my m8's.  I goto Monk's Walk School, and, have
been Captain of the Cricket Team.  Cricket is my favourite sport ya see. :)
Hm.... Well, I enjoy reading, and watching TV.  I love Star Trek and the
X-Files, and Game On, along with anything else funny on TV. (Red Dwarf
etc.)  I'm really into computers.  I use an AMIGA 1200 ( see my system spec
@{"here" link Computer} ;) ).  I love the 'net.
  My favourite part of the 'net HAS to be IRC :). 
I use the nick of ^Bradman^, and I use EFnet, Undernet DALnet :).
Hm... I like using @{"BBS's" link BBS} as well :).  Well, that's about it
for now!


@ENDNODE

